{"tid":976471,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「韓大勢女團」爸爆性侵女職員！　網友找出線索崩潰：T女團嗎？","createTime":"2019-01-10T12:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T05:09:43.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0431c549bfccd8b3a2782987626523ffac726a45","tid":976471,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"南韓性侵事件層出不窮！韓媒10日一早先是爆出，19歲童星鄭惟安涉嫌性騷擾，晚間又有廚師A某被爆對餐廳職員伸出魔爪， 女職員崩潰向警方報警，消息才因此曝光於大眾之前，由於A某有位大名鼎鼎的歌手女兒，報導登上南韓熱搜，震驚所有網友。<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報導，A某身為餐廳廚師，在某天工作時對餐廳女職員性侵得逞，且A某不只伸出一次魔爪，女職員9月崩潰向警方報警，全案正在調查中。案件直到10日爆發，警方表示，目前還沒有確切的證據，仍在調查中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3824/d3824983.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3824%2Fd3824983.jpg&h=3b56038d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲韓網友掀出報導的蛛絲馬跡，公佈女團成員以及爸爸出演的節目 。（圖／翻攝自JTBC、never）<br />\n<br />\n然而，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">報導把A某的身份曝光，他的女兒是相當有人氣的女團成員，且曾經在節目上出演過，有網民掀出報導裡的蛛絲馬跡，比對出T團的22歲成員的爸爸也曾以廚師身份在節目中亮相</span></strong>，不過也有網友表示，調查還沒結束，等官方說明才准。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要估人了"},{"pid":"ce4712725861be1422e7751a1231724b18ebd7c9","tid":976471,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:03:35.000Z","msg":"定延？"},{"pid":"98f63e7e3de2527f72d520c9155e6b24503a5f8c","tid":976471,"uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:03:51.000Z","msg":"定延老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c36c5cd2cb49ae5f649db22a429c6005fd9c530","tid":976471,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:04:03.000Z","msg":"如果係真既話會唔會係kpop界福音？"},{"pid":"f19df6859acbeda2a730f25567b2635fecabfaa7","tid":976471,"uid":74065,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.kpopn.com/wp-content/uploads/old-post-images/2016/08/20160816-yeon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kpopn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fold-post-images%2F2016%2F08%2F20160816-yeon.jpg&h=038f5c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孔昇延與定延的父親俞昌俊 (유창준，音譯) 是一名廚師！<br />\n「歡迎無論法式料理、韓食、日本料理或中華料理都得心應手，有25年經驗的廚師 &minus; 俞昌俊！」<br />\n<br />\n而俞昌俊除了在節目中大展精湛的廚藝與 Sam Kim 主廚對決外，也談到關於自己因為大女兒是演員孔昇延、小女兒是 TWICE 成員定延，而被大眾稱作「國民岳父」的話題，並表示自己與一般爸爸一樣，很難接受女兒帶男友回家！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672fb49c456ff842479b802f2bf6e26e75476681","tid":976471,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:04:44.000Z","msg":"唔理炒唔炒車了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fc583183925feca35160f1b7e7643b4d408395","tid":976471,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家追追追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4283056133f7276bacf8a42890839f2aa08a1c6","tid":976471,"uid":26833,"like":1,"